# Secure Code, SCA, SAST and Secret Detection

## Objective

This project demonstrates how to identify vulnerable dependencies, insecure code patterns, and exposed secrets before code reaches production.

## Scope

The assessment includes:

- Static Application Security Testing
- Software Composition Analysis
- Secret detection
- Secure code review
- CI/CD security checks

## Tools Used

- GitHub Actions
- Semgrep
- Gitleaks
- Trivy
- OWASP Dependency-Check

